866
00:51:41.571 --> 00:51:45.009
<font color="#ffffff">Was passiert?</font>

867
00:51:45.651 --> 00:51:49.189
<font color="#ffffff">Der Markt fragt Bio-Eier nach.</font>

868
00:51:49.831 --> 00:51:52.470
